parameters: 'シャーク大公はAV女優！？敗北の代償…の巻'

Memimi: *cough*... I-I can still fight... I refuse to lose
to someone like you...

Orca Mayor: Tough girl... At this rate, we'll never get
anywhere, huh? Hey, Drillmaid! Hold her down...

Drillmaid: Drill-drill! Don't you move now? Playtime's over,
you'd better give up quickly...

Shark Broccoli: To interfere in a fair fight... You really
have changed, Orca Asparagus... no, Orca Mayor...

Orca Mayor: That's right, if only you had shown up from the
start! Everything changed when our costume wrestling group
went under... Now, I've lost my Asparagus too... I am the
invincible monster, Orca Mayor!!!

Shark Broccoli: Ugh...! Shark Duke... now is the time to
escape...!

Memimi: Ahhh... no way! Lord Shark Broccoli... it can't be
true...

Orca Mayor: This is the end for you!! I've longed for this
day, to return the favor from the mayoral battle five years
ago!! I'll quell the throbbing pain of my lost Asparagus
with this!!

Memimi: Uwaaaaaaaahhhhh!!! Lord Shark Broccoli
aaaaaahhhhh!!!

Orca Broccoli Mayor: With this, I am now Orca Broccoli
Mayor!! Now, as for my complete victory... I'll take the
secret recipe for that delicious powder and the custody of
that little girl over there...

Shark Broccoli: Ugh... run away... Shark Duke... You're
still young, it's too early for you to be sullied... Leave
Mudgain City... live a normal life somewhere else...

Memimi: Anomalocaris! Take Lord Shark Broccoli outside the
venue! Cerberus Octopus, clear our escape route!! I'll hold
this one off!

Memimi: The Monster Fight isn't over yet...! By the time you
defeat me, Lord Shark Broccoli, the only one who knows the
powder formula, will have escaped. Hahaha, too bad, but
you'll have to settle for my AV debut as your victory
prize!!!

Orca Broccoli Mayor: ...You've got some nerve... It won't
take long to find that wounded shark and extract the formula
from him... but first, I really want to break that
unnecessarily spirited heart of yours completely!!

Memimi: (This is fine... Lord Shark Broccoli... as long as
you are safe, I have... repaid a little of the debt for
picking me up...)

And so, for Memimi and the members of the dark organization,
an era of darkness began...
